We was three clerics chain casting CH on the main tank.<br>
<br>
First cleric starts casting<br>
3.5 secs after 1st cleric, 2nd cleric start casting.<br>
3.5 secs after 2nd cleric, 3rd cleric start casting.<br>
<br>
On this way the MT/MA will get a CH every 3.5 secs. (except the first CH of course which will take CH. So CHs needed to be cast before the fight starts.)<br>
This is a great method and well needed against higher/boss mobs.<br>
<br>
CH takes 400mana.<br>
Another good spell to help this is Divine Intervention.<br>
There is some % chance (donno how many %) that this spell do a CH on the person if he reach 0hps under a 10min time.<br>
Costs 500mana and lasts 10min.<br>
